<h5 id="subject_748941">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=d02c2b8ebfdf44378e526f6c0f474323&amp;topic=79058.msg748941#msg748941" rel="nofollow">Re: 【暗影狂奔第五版核心规则书翻译】 p.417 武器评价词汇</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
